Reclusa::

She turned and looked at the other bot. "Hmmm, so I see and understand
how you have thought this out thoroughly. Many like one, all the
others under control with little to no free will of thier own. Hmmm,
yes, you have a superior intelect than most bots I have encountered."
 She gave him an approving smile. "I would like for you to contact
Hydras and inform him of this. He would not only be very impressed,
but greatly satisfied in your work."
